description: As User I should be able to manage booking

steps.name: Given  I navigate to the PO Ferries Freight Website
And  I click the Book Now Link
And  I successfully login cash user
When  I click the Book Link
And  I click Route dropdown
And  I select Cairnryan Larne Route
And  I select Date for Route
And  I click Number of passengers dropdown
And  I select Number of passengers
And  I click Continue Booking
And  I click Unit Type
And  I enter Vehicle registration number
And  I enter Vehicle length
And  I click Step Two Continue
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Unit ID
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Length
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Height
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Width
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Weight
And  I verify Review booking details Vehicle Passengers
And  I agree Terms and Conditions
And  I click Proceed to payment
And  I verify booking Amount
And  I enter Card Number
And  I click Expiry Date Month
And  I Select Expiry Date Month
And  I click Expiry Date Year
And  I Select Expiry Date Year
And  I enter CSC
And  I click Submit button
And  I Verify Journey Details
